                  <li><strong>FHA Loans</strong>: Our tool factors in both upfront and annual Mortgage Insurance Premiums (MIP).</li>
                  <li><strong>VA Loans</strong>: Designed for veterans, this calculation excludes PMI but integrates the mandatory VA funding fee.</li>
