              <div class="mt-3 text-xs sm:text-sm text-neutral-555 dark:text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed pl-8 pr-4 space-y-3">
                <p>
                  A refinance makes sense if your new interest rate is low enough to offset your closing costs. You can use this tool to calculate your break-even point for a traditional rate-and-term refinance, a cash-out refinance, or even evaluate senior-specific options like a reverse mortgage (HECM).
